&lt;/audio> 
&lt;p>विश्वेश्वराय नरकार्णवतारणाय कर्णामृताय शशिशेखरभूषणाय । &lt;br>
कर्पूरकुन्दधवलाय जटाधराय दारिद्र्य दुःखदहनाय नमः शिवाय ॥ १॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Shiva Shadakshara Stotram - शिवषडाक्षर स्तोत्रं</title><link>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/shiva-shadakshara-stotram/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/shiva-shadakshara-stotram/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/samskrut/Shiva.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="शवषडकषर-सततर">शिवषडाक्षर स्तोत्रं&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e0%a4%b6%e0%a4%b5%e0%a4%b7%e0%a4%a1%e0%a4%95%e0%a4%b7%e0%a4%b0-%e0%a4%b8%e0%a4%a4%e0%a4%a4%e0%a4%b0" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="shiva-shadakshara-stotram">Shiva Shadakshara Stotram&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#shiva-shadakshara-stotram" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
 &lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/022-ShivShadaksharaStotram.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
 Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio> 
&lt;p>ॐकारं बिंदुसंयुक्तं नित्यं ध्यायंति योगिनः । &lt;br>
कामदं मोक्षदं चैव ॐकाराय नमो नमः ॥१॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Shivmaanaspooja - शिवमानसपूजा</title><link>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/shivmaanaspooja/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/shivmaanaspooja/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/samskrut/Shiva.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="शवमनसपज">शिवमानसपूजा&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e0%a4%b6%e0%a4%b5%e0%a4%ae%e0%a4%a8%e0%a4%b8%e0%a4%aa%e0%a4%9c" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="shivmaanaspooja">Shivmaanaspooja&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#shivmaanaspooja" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
 &lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/006-ShivMaanasPooja.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
 Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio> 
&lt;p>रत्नैः कल्पितमासनं हिमजलैः स्नानं च दिव्याम्बरं &lt;br>
नानारत्नविभूषितं मृगमदामोदाङ्कितं चन्दनम् । &lt;br>
जातीचम्पकबिल्वपत्ररचितं पुष्पं च धूपं तथा &lt;br>
दीपं देव दयानिधे पशुपते हृत्कल्पितं गृह्यताम् ॥१॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Shri Shivpanchaakshari Stotram - श्रीशिवपञ्चाक्षरस्तोत्रम्</title><link>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/shri-shivpanchaakshari-stotram/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/shri-shivpanchaakshari-stotram/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/samskrut/Shiva.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="शरशवपञचकषरसततरम">श्रीशिवपञ्चाक्षरस्तोत्रम्&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e0%a4%b6%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%b6%e0%a4%b5%e0%a4%aa%e0%a4%9e%e0%a4%9a%e0%a4%95%e0%a4%b7%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%b8%e0%a4%a4%e0%a4%a4%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%ae" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="shri-shivpanchaakshari-stotram">Shri Shivpanchaakshari Stotram&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#shri-shivpanchaakshari-stotram" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
 &lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/023-ShivPanchaAkshari.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
 Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio> 
&lt;p>नागेन्द्रहाराय त्रिलोचनाय, &lt;br>
भस्माङ्गरागाय महेश्वराय । &lt;br>
नित्याय शुद्धाय दिगम्बराय, &lt;br>
तस्मै न काराय नमः शिवाय ॥१॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Uma Maheshwara Stotram - उमामहेश्वर स्तोत्रं</title><link>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/uma-maheshwara-stotram/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/uma-maheshwara-stotram/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/samskrut/Umamaheshwar.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="उममहशवर-सततर">उमामहेश्वर स्तोत्रं&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e0%a4%89%e0%a4%ae%e0%a4%ae%e0%a4%b9%e0%a4%b6%e0%a4%b5%e0%a4%b0-%e0%a4%b8%e0%a4%a4%e0%a4%a4%e0%a4%b0" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="uma-maheshwara-stotram">Uma Maheshwara Stotram&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#uma-maheshwara-stotram" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
 &lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/024-UmaMaheshwarStotram.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
 Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio> 
&lt;p>नमः शिवाभ्यां नवयौवनाभ्यां &lt;br>
परस्पराश्लिष्टवपुर्धराभ्यां | &lt;br>
नगेन्द्रकन्यावृषकेतनाभ्यां &lt;br>
नमो नमः शङ्करपार्वतीभ्यां || 1 ||&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Shri Kaal Bhairav Ashtakam - श्री काल भैरव अष्टकम्‌</title><link>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/shri-kaal-bhairav-ashta/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/shri-kaal-bhairav-ashta/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/samskrut/Shiva.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="शर-कल-भरव-अषटकम">श्री काल भैरव अष्टकम्‌&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e0%a4%b6%e0%a4%b0-%e0%a4%95%e0%a4%b2-%e0%a4%ad%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%b5-%e0%a4%85%e0%a4%b7%e0%a4%9f%e0%a4%95%e0%a4%ae" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="shri-kaal-bhairav-ashtakam">Shri Kaal Bhairav Ashtakam&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#shri-kaal-bhairav-ashtakam" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
 &lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/014-KaalBhairavAshtakam.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
 Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio> 
&lt;p>देवराज सेव्यमान पावनाङ्घ्रि पङ्कजं &lt;br>
व्यालयज्ञ सूत्रमिन्दु शेखरं कृपाकरम्‌ । &lt;br>
नारदादि योगिबृन्द वन्दितं दिगम्बरं &lt;br>
काशिकापुराधिनाथ कालभेरवं भजे ॥ 1 ॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>RudraPrashna LaghuNyasa - रुद्रप्रश्नः लघुन्यासः</title><link>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/rudraprashna-laghunyasa/</link><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/rudraprashna-laghunyasa/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/samskrut/Rudra.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="रदरपरशन-लघनयस">रुद्रप्रश्नः लघुन्यासः&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%a6%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%aa%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%b6%e0%a4%a8-%e0%a4%b2%e0%a4%98%e0%a4%a8%e0%a4%af%e0%a4%b8" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="rudraprashna-laghunyasa">RudraPrashna LaghuNyasa&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#rudraprashna-laghunyasa" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
 &lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/020-RudraPrashnaLagu.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
 Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio> 
&lt;p>ॐ अथात्मानग्ं शिवात्मानग् श्रीरुद्ररूपं ध्यायेत् ॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>रुद्रप्रश्नः लघुन्यासः &lt;br>
शुद्धस्फटिकसंकाशं त्रिनेत्रं पञ्चवक्त्रकम् । &lt;br>
गङ्गाधरं दशभुजं सर्वाभरणभूषितम् ॥ &lt;br>
नीलग्रीवं शशाङ्काङ्कं नागयज्ञोपवीतिनम् । &lt;br>
व्याघ्रचर्मोत्तरीयं च वरेण्यमभयप्रदम् ॥ &lt;br>
कमण्डल्वक्षसूत्राणां धारिणं शूलपाणिनम् । &lt;br>
ज्वलन्तं पिङ्गलजटा-शिखामुद्योतधारिणम् ॥ &lt;br>
वृषस्कन्ध-समारूढम् उमादेहार्ध-धारिणम् । &lt;br>
अमृतेनाप्लुतं शान्तं दिव्यभोगसमन्वितम् ॥ &lt;br>
दिग्देवतासमायुक्तं सुरासुरनमस्कृतम् । &lt;br>
नित्यंच शाश्वतं शुद्धं ध्रुवमक्षरमव्ययम् ॥ &lt;br>
सर्वव्यापिनमीशानं रुद्रं वै विश्वरूपिणम् । &lt;br>
एवं ध्यात्वा द्विजसम्यक् ततो यजनमारभेत् ॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>NamamishMisan - नमामीशमीसान निर्वाणरूपं</title><link>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/namamishmishan-nirvan-roopam/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Jan 2010 14:33:35 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/namamishmishan-nirvan-roopam/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/samskrut/Rudra.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="नममशमसन-नरवणरप">नमामीशमीसान निर्वाणरूपं&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e0%a4%a8%e0%a4%ae%e0%a4%ae%e0%a4%b6%e0%a4%ae%e0%a4%b8%e0%a4%a8-%e0%a4%a8%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%b5%e0%a4%a3%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%aa" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;audio controls>
 &lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/003-Namamish.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
 Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio>
&lt;p>नमामीशमीशान निर्वाणरूपं। विभुं व्यापकं ब्रह्मवेदस्वरूपम्।।&lt;/p>
&lt;p>निजं निर्गुणं निर्विकल्पं निरीहं। चिदाकाशमाकाशवासं भजेऽहं।।&lt;/p>
&lt;p>निराकारमोंकारमूलं तुरीयं। गिरा ग्यान गोतीतमीशं गिरीशं।।&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>